content: For weekdays, I'd like to wake up at 7:15 am, and on weekends, I'd like to wake up at 8:00 am. As for my current sleep schedule, I usually go to bed at 11:00 pm every night, and on weekdays, I wake up at 7:15 am, but on weekends, it varies - like I mentioned, on the previous Saturday, I woke up at 7:30 am, and last Saturday, I woke up at 9:30 am.
